{"tid":1252688,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[大香港MMO] 2種新職業 - 雨遮支援師 / 光之術士","createTime":"2019-06-23T06:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-23T06:57:56.000Z","uid":179379,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7719140fe6d5f44f7ec5c03cd23a6114a8cb6b94","tid":1252688,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:46:34.000Z","msg":"兩種新職業專為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">中至新手</span></span>而設<br />\n屬於<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">輔助型</span></span>職業<br />\n適合<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">未刷裝</span></span>之玩家參與副本提升經驗值<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 雨遮支援師</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fL1EoVk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfL1EoVk.jpg&h=82204c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡介：為同路人遮風擋風<br />\n特色：於同伴發動技能期間，為其提供<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">保護罩</span></span>，協助抵擋<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">攝魂者</span></span>之攻擊，對<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">赤屬性攝魂者</span></span>最為有效<br />\n基本裝備：<br />\n- Cap帽 (魔防+2)<br />\n- 太陽眼鏡 (魔防+2)<br />\n- 口罩 (魔防+1)<br />\n- 雨遮 (物攻+1, 物防+1, 魔防+1)<br />\n備注：雨遮支援技能效果<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">可以加乘</span></span>，即<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">愈多人</span></span>同時發動支援技能，<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">效果愈為顯著</span></span><br />\n<br />\n高經驗可升級為<br />\n- 雙手雨遮支援師 (支援效果加倍)<br />\n- 赤系攝魂追擊者 (針對赤屬性攝魂者效果提升)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 光之術士</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vGc4z14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvGc4z14.jpg&h=9934c1f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n簡介：以光淨化一切惡魔<br />\n特色：使用<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">光屬性魔法</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">降低</span></span>敵人<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">命中率</span></span>及<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">士氣</span></span><br />\n基本裝備：<br />\n- Cap帽 (魔防+2)<br />\n- 太陽眼鏡 (魔防+2)<br />\n- 口罩 (魔防+1)<br />\n- 光屬性魔法杖 (魔攻+3)<br />\n<br />\n高經驗可級為<br />\n- 強光之術士 (範圍較大)<br />\n- 激光之術士 (效果較高)<br />\n備注：激光魔法有機會<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">直接對敵方扣成傷害</span></span>，可能會成為<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵方攻擊及追捕目標</span></span>，如要使用敬請小心為上"},{"pid":"0057e3f85be408165129d4c04eb959988151e9dd","tid":1252688,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:51:25.000Z","msg":"同時推出限時<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">時裝</span></span>道具<br />\n可以於<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">打副本</span></span>時裝飾你嘅裝備<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">1. 皺紋膠紙</span></span> (時限較短)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MiQNxZa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMiQNxZa.jpg&h=17d869ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">2. 醫生膠布</span></span> (時限較長)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1y5UXq8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1y5UXq8.jpg&h=c0560ee6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2f671841ff0ce30131f0d2da87fe2dd9909c5808","tid":1252688,"uid":179379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-23T06:52:13.000Z","msg":"屌 開錯台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我想開遊戲台㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d86ebdde223d3ca851ee7935251e005cba92197","tid":1252688,"uid":209689,"like":0